1.title: Episode #1.1

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

1.plot: Do Min Joon, an alien who landed in Korea 400 years ago, discovers that he has three months left on Earth. And that is when he meets Cheon Song Yi, the biggest Hallyu star in Korea.

2.title: Episode #1.2

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

2.plot: Min Joon embarrasses Song Yi in public while she films for a documentary special about her daily life.

3.title: Episode #1.3

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

3.plot: Song Yi suffers from appendicitis, and forces Min Joon to take her to the hospital. He takes the opportunity to protect her from his premonition.

4.title: Episode #1.4

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

4.plot: When an actress dies from an accident, Song Yi is immediately the target for blame. She seeks refuge in Min Joon's apartment, uncovering secrets that he'd like to keep buried.

5.title: Episode #1.5

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

5.plot: Song Yi hides away in Min Joon's apartment after the suspicious death of fellow actress Han Yoo Ra. Prosecutor Yoo Suk begins an investigation to look into whether her death was a suicide or not.

6.title: Episode #1.6

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

6.plot: Following the Han Yoo Ra scandal, Song Yi postpones renewing her contract with her management.

7.title: Episode #1.7

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

7.plot: As the threats intensify, Song Yi turns to Min Joon for help. He slowly becomes more human-like by being around her so often, and agrees to be her temporary manager.

8.title: Episode #1.8

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

8.plot: Song Yi thinks stress is contributing to her "hallucinations" of Min Joon saving her. The investigation intensifies as witnesses to Jae Kyung and Yoo Ra's relationship begins to disappear.

9.title: Episode #1.9

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

9.plot: Min Joon gets sick after he shares a kiss with Song Yi. Se Mi decides to finally meet Min Joon for herself.

10.title: Episode #1.10

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

10.plot: Song Yi has difficulty dealing with her feelings for Min Joon, who's also trying to distance himself from her and not reveal his true nature to anyone.

11.title: Episode #1.11

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

11.plot: Jae Kyung will go at any length to get Song Yi and Min Joon, while Hee Kyung begins to view his brother in a different light.

12.title: Episode #1.12

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

12.plot: Song Yi refuses to hear what Se Mi has to say about her savior from 12 years ago. Min Joon recovers from his injuries but realizes that his heart is now broken.

13.title: Episode #1.13

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

13.plot: Min Joon does his best to distance himself from Song Yi and holds up his end of the deal with Jae Kyung.

14.title: Episode #1.14

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

14.plot: When Song Yi's wires break while shooting, it's a game to the death with no holds barred between Min Joon and Jae Kyung.

15.title: Episode #1.15

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

15.plot: Song Yi recovers from her injuries but Hee Kyung is still in a coma. Min Joon can't stay away from protecting Song Yi.

16.title: Episode #1.16

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

16.plot: Min Joon and Song Yi admit their feelings for one another and start dating, but his departure date looms near.

17.title: Episode #1.17

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

17.plot: Hee Kyung won't stop until he finds his sister-in-law and uncovers his brother's dark secrets. Song Yi and Min Joon can't deal with the fact that he'll need to leave in a month.

18.title: Episode #1.18

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

18.plot: Min Joon's powers weaken as he stays on Earth longer than he should. Hee Kyung discovers his brother's true self but it will be more difficult than it seems to have him pay for his crimes.

19.title: Episode #1.19

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

19.plot: Hee Kyung must find a way to stop Jae Kyung before he himself ends up on his brother's hit list. Song Yi discovers the price Min Joon must pay if he stays with her.

20.title: Episode #1.20

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

20.plot: With one week left before he leaves, Song Yi and Min Joon spend each day as if they had seventy more years left together.

21.title: Episode #1.21

episode of.title: You Who Came from the Stars (TV Series 2013–2014)

21.plot: Do Min Joon's departure is too difficult to bear for Song Yi, even three years later.

imdb.title: You Who Came from the Stars
plot: Do Min-Joon, an alien that came to our planet 400 years ago, will be able to return to his planet in 3 months, but when he meets famous actress Chun Song-Yi, all the centuries he spent distancing himself from humans come to an end.::Dama del Puente
synopsis: The story revolves around relationship of Do Min - Joon (Soo Hyun Kim), a man who came on earth from outer space 400 years ago and Cheon Song - Yi (Gianna Jun), famous actress with hard character, who resembles a girl who Do Min - Joon met when he came on our planet. They cross their roads by becoming neighbours. Do Min - Joon, who isn't a communicative person, is still dragged into dangerous and comic situations with Cheon Song - Yi, while feeling mystical connection between her and the girl he met 400 years ago. By time, he develops romantic feelings towards her, but is trying to deny it because he does not believe in love. Though, while series develope, he starts protecting her from a man who tries to kill her. He has left only 3 months time on earth and is starting to have doubts about if he really wants to go back or not. He takes advises of his only friend lawyer who he saved 30 years ago. Cheon Song - Yi is in love with a man who saved her twelve years ago but doesn't even remember his face. Ironically, this mysterious man appears to be Do Min - Joon.
